translated: Karim Djellabi is a French footballer of Algerian origin born May 31, 1983 in Epinay-sous-Bois in the department of Seine-Saint-Denis (93).
original: Karim Djellabi est un footballeur français d'origine algérienne né le 31 mai 1983 à Epinay-sous-Bois dans le département de la Seine-Saint-Denis (93).
